question.text: "Boss, what’s IBOX? I don’t understand"

languages.en: "Boss, what’s IBOX? I don’t understand"
languages.ms: "Boss, apa itu IBOX? Saya tak faham"

detailed.en: "IBOX: If the number rotates 24 times, buy IBOX for RM1 to get 24 number combinations, 24 ÷ RM1 = RM0.04 per number. IBOX = ÷, 1234 = 24 combinations, 1134 = 12, 1133 = 6, 1113 = 4"
detailed.ms:
"IBOX
Jika Nombor Pusingan 24 kali
Beli IBOX Bayar RM1 Saja Boleh Dapat 24 Pasang Nombor
24 ÷ RM1 ＝ Rm0.04 Satu Nombor
IBOX = ÷
1234 =24 Pasang
1134 =12 Pasang
1133 =6 Pasang
1113 =4 Pasang"
detailed.cn: "IBOX：如果號碼旋轉24次，買IBOX只需付1令吉可得24組號碼，24 ÷ 1令吉 = 每組0.04令吉。IBOX = ÷，1234 = 24組，1134 = 12組，1133 = 6組，1113 = 4組"

question.text: "Boss, how is the match calculated?"

languages.en: "Boss, how is the match calculated?"
languages.ms: "Boss, kiraan match ikut apa?"

detailed.en:
"WE WILL FOLLOW THE SCORE OF 90MIN + INJURY TIME ONLY (DOES NOT INCLUDE 15min+15min extra time and penalties after extra time)
COUNT
(0-45min + injury time)
(45-90min + injury time)
DO NOT COUNT
(90-120MIN EXTRA TIME)
PENALTIES AFTER 90mins & 120mins"
detailed.ms:
"KAMI AKAN IKUT SKOR 90MIN + INJURY TIME SAHAJA ( TIDAK TERMASUK 15min+15min extra time dan penalty lepas extra time )
KIRA
(0-45min + injury time)
(45-90min + injury time)
X KIRA
(90-120MIN EXTRA TIME)
PENALTY LEPAS 90mins & 120mins"
detailed.cn:
"我們只按90分鐘+傷停時間的比分計算（不包括15分鐘+15分鐘加時和加時後的點球）
計算：
(0-45分鐘+傷停時間)
(45-90分鐘+傷停時間)
